#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:2 5b38ad7aab8842559db887601bec4de2
msgid "Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:4 4f85b83c791845e8924fedd01397a930
msgid ""
"TensorMesh is a finite-element library written from the ground up for "
"PyTorch. A :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` is an :class:`torch.nn.Module`, weak "
"forms are plain ``forward`` methods that receive basis tensors, and every "
"linear solve is a differentiable op. The same code that solves a Poisson "
"problem on a laptop CPU also runs on a GPU and backpropagates through to a "
"learnable parameter — without changing the FEM logic."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 是一个从底层为 PyTorch 打造的有限元库。\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 就是一个 "
":class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ ，弱形式只是接收基函数张量的普通 ``forward`` "
"方法，而每一次线性求解都是可微的算子。同一份求解笔记本 CPU 上泊松问题的代码，也能在 GPU "
"上运行，并将梯度反向传播到可学习参数——无需改动任何有限元逻辑。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:12 8166a7f4cb704b9caad25aa9f2456440
msgid ""
"This page is the mental model: how the modules fit together and the design "
"principles behind those choices."
msgstr "本页给出一套心智模型：各模块如何协同工作，以及这些选择背后的设计原则。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:17 ddb2c87e6c0d4f5287d574f9d80f0cd9
msgid "The FEM workflow"
msgstr "有限元方法工作流"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:19 47ec64cc5eb6460fba3b961c454fa388
msgid "Solving a PDE in TensorMesh follows one canonical pipeline:"
msgstr "在 TensorMesh 中求解偏微分方程遵循一条标准流水线："

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:25 222f30de54074c578e2ddaa1ab1fffa1
msgid "**Mesh** discretizes the domain into points and cells."
msgstr "**Mesh** 将求解域离散为点和网格单元。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:26 7ea961fd427146d0adf22c56d1dd03fb
msgid ""
"**Assembler** turns a weak form (``a(u, v)`` or ``l(v)``) into a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` or load vector."
msgstr ""
"**Assembler** 将弱形式（\\ ``a(u, v)`` 或 ``l(v)``\\ ）转化为 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` 或载荷向量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:28 e1c1f30845af4f60b8997dfa38714ce6
msgid ""
"**Condenser** applies Dirichlet boundary conditions by static condensation, "
"producing a reduced system on the interior DOFs."
msgstr "**Condenser** 通过静态凝聚施加狄利克雷边界条件，得到一个仅含内部自由度的缩减系统。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:30 52275ce56bf843eda4207c787a688a80
msgid ""
"**Solve** dispatches the reduced system to a sparse-linear-algebra backend "
"(via the :doc:`torch-sla <linear_solvers>` package)."
msgstr "**Solve** 将缩减系统分派给某个稀疏线性代数后端（通过 :doc:`torch-sla <linear_solvers>` 包）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:33 fb026b6e6d1545e382992f2db841c2e8
msgid ""
"The :doc:`../getting_started/quickstart` walks through this pipeline end-to-"
"end in about 30 lines of Python. Each subsequent chapter of this guide zooms"
" in on one stage."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../getting_started/quickstart` 用大约 30 行 Python "
"端到端地走完这条流水线。本指南后续的每一章都会聚焦于其中一个阶段。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:39 e3390105b320488ba8d1893ee5dcc127
msgid "Module map"
msgstr "模块全景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:41 22a6a6bd1a1b44c4b09938c786eac5ec
msgid ""
"The library splits cleanly along the pipeline. The arrows show data flow, "
"not import direction:"
msgstr "整个库沿流水线清晰划分。箭头表示数据流向，而非导入方向："

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:60 c61767d11b8a488981e34358b0fb74d8
msgid "What lives in each module:"
msgstr "每个模块包含的内容："

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:62 785b16c8b36a463cb0decd170f7e977f
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.mesh` — :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` and its built-in "
"generators (``gen_rectangle``, ``gen_circle``, ``gen_cube``, …); meshio I/O;"
" adjacency, partitioning, and graph coloring helpers."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.mesh` —— :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 及其内置生成器（\\ "
"``gen_rectangle``\\ 、\\ ``gen_circle``\\ 、\\ ``gen_cube`` 等）；meshio "
"输入/输出；邻接、分区与图着色辅助工具。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:65 8bb93dc9308844fd9271be6aa46fbef4
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.element` — reference shapes (:class:`~tensormesh.Triangle`,"
" :class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`, :class:`~tensormesh.Tetrahedron`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`, :class:`~tensormesh.Prism`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`, :class:`~tensormesh.Line`), basis evaluation, "
"quadrature rules, and the Gmsh/VTK ↔ TensorMesh ordering convention."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.element` —— 参考单元形状（\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Triangle`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Quadrilateral`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Tetrahedron`\\ "
"、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Hexahedron`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Prism`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.Pyramid`\\ 、\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Line`\\ "
"）、基函数求值、求积规则，以及 Gmsh/VTK ↔ TensorMesh 排序约定。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:71 a050fe478b2f416bb382ab30f4d5f033
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.assemble` — the three weak-form base classes "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`, :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`, "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`, plus built-ins for the most common "
"forms (Laplace, mass, linear elasticity, Neo-Hookean, …)."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.assemble` —— 三个弱形式基类 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`\\ 、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`\\ ，以及针对最常见弱形式（Laplace、质量、线弹性、新胡克等）的内置实现。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:76 f3f2b4031a404e80968e106033f3f497
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.sparse` — :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` "
"(subclass of ``torch_sla.SparseTensor``), so linear systems are solved by "
"``K.solve(b)`` and nonlinear systems by ``K.nonlinear_solve(residual, u0, "
"*params)``, dispatched through ``torch-sla``. The in-tree ``spsolve`` / "
":func:`~tensormesh.sparse.nonlinear_solve` free functions are legacy entry "
"points scheduled for removal."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.sparse` —— :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ （\\ "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor`` 的子类），因此线性系统通过 ``K.solve(b)`` 求解、非线性系统通过 "
"``K.nonlinear_solve(residual, u0, *params)`` 求解，二者均由 ``torch-sla`` 分派。库内自带的 "
"``spsolve`` / :func:`~tensormesh.sparse.nonlinear_solve` 自由函数是遗留入口点，已计划移除。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:83 c4fe5e0dd57c4c2aa9394c8687cecb92
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.operator` — :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` for Dirichlet "
"BCs via static condensation."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.operator` —— :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ "
"，用于通过静态凝聚施加狄利克雷边界条件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:85 f671df151f054db185be5b7db4bee781
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.ode` — explicit and implicit-linear time integrators "
"(Euler, midpoint, Runge-Kutta) for transient problems."
msgstr ":mod:`tensormesh.ode` —— 用于瞬态问题的显式与隐式线性时间积分器（Euler、中点法、龙格-库塔）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:87 2343aa9afd7f49f3b2fe84e908e83347
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.functional` — Voigt elasticity helpers, strain / stress, "
"and other tensor utilities used inside ``forward`` methods."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.functional` —— Voigt 弹性辅助函数、应变 / 应力，以及其他在 ``forward`` "
"方法内部使用的张量工具。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:89 33f80b2f5a004229b68db42ed8f973e7
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.dataset` — :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen` and pre-built "
"multi-frequency equation classes for generating training datasets."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.dataset` —— :class:`~tensormesh.MeshGen` "
"以及用于生成训练数据集的预置多频方程类。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:91 54142c381658487c92086369c9c37508
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.material` — :class:`~tensormesh.material.IsotropicMaterial`"
" and library presets (Steel, Aluminum, Rubber, Glass)."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.material` —— "
":class:`~tensormesh.material.IsotropicMaterial` "
"以及材料库预设（Steel、Aluminum、Rubber、Glass）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:94 fd7d9cd9ca9947e08ccd731aa279b8f6
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.optimizer` — :class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer` "
"(Optimality Criteria) for compliance-based topology optimization."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.optimizer` —— :class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer`\\ "
"（最优性准则法），用于基于柔度的拓扑优化。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:96 667e0facb6fe4b48a44c2c838d38ad92
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.visualization` — matplotlib (2D) and PyVista (3D) backends;"
" lazily imported by :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.plot`."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.visualization` —— matplotlib（2D）与 PyVista（3D）后端；由 "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.plot` 延迟导入。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:98 67a623e0c6b44ba49682f330ad1ce5c2
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.distributed` — graph-partitioned distributed assembly "
"across multiple ranks (advanced; see the example gallery)."
msgstr ":mod:`tensormesh.distributed` —— 跨多个进程（rank）的图分区分布式装配（高级特性；参见示例库）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:101 46bf9f878d4c4574aa18270d01fdcebc
msgid ""
"The sparse-linear-algebra stack (``SparseMatrix``, ``.solve`` / "
"``.nonlinear_solve``, gradient-aware adjoint backward) is delegated to a "
"separate package, `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_, and shared with "
"other projects in the same ecosystem."
msgstr ""
"稀疏线性代数栈（\\ ``SparseMatrix``\\ 、\\ ``.solve`` / ``.nonlinear_solve``\\ "
"、感知梯度的伴随反向传播）被委托给一个独立的包 `torch-sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_\\ "
"，并与同一生态系统中的其他项目共享。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:109 13c89091a81944e7b3af96bf88124978
msgid "Design principles"
msgstr "设计原则"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:111 2d9793507f9f4fe6ab8d029a33352f86
msgid ""
"**PyTorch-native.** :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` extends "
":class:`torch.nn.Module`. Its ``points`` and per-element connectivity are "
"buffers; per-node fields are buffers too. Assemblers are also ``nn.Module`` "
"s. There is no separate \"FEM kernel\" abstraction layer — everything is a "
"tensor that flows through familiar PyTorch machinery (``.to(device)``, "
"``.double()``, ``state_dict``, autograd, JIT tracing)."
msgstr ""
"**PyTorch 原生。** :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 继承自 :class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ 。它的"
" ``points`` 与逐单元连接性都是 buffer；逐节点字段同样是 buffer。装配器本身也是 ``nn.Module``\\ "
"。这里没有单独的“有限元内核”抽象层——一切都是张量，流经我们熟悉的 PyTorch 机制（\\ ``.to(device)``\\ 、\\ "
"``.double()``\\ 、\\ ``state_dict``\\ 、autograd、JIT 追踪）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:119 b16126243e85407f943280a9ba96e2f1
msgid ""
"**Weak forms in pure Python.** The only PDE-specific code a user writes is a"
" ``forward`` method that returns the integrand at the quadrature points:"
msgstr ""
"**纯 Python 弱形式。** 用户唯一需要编写的、与具体偏微分方程相关的代码，就是一个返回求积点处被积函数的 ``forward`` 方法："

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:129 7e4d3f5634044d79af5b8a375dd603a1
msgid ""
"The library handles reference-element evaluation, geometry, quadrature "
"weights, and the global assemble-into-sparse step. The same pattern works "
"for load vectors (:class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`) and boundary integrals"
" (:class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`)."
msgstr ""
"库会负责参考单元求值、几何、求积权重，以及全局装配到稀疏矩阵的步骤。同样的模式也适用于载荷向量（\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`\\ ）和边界积分（\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:134 a83c615ff79043b3baeb5fc7936c82c9
msgid ""
"**Tensorized assembly.** There is no Python-level loop over elements. Inside"
" ``__call__``, basis functions and quadrature points are evaluated once for "
"the whole mesh; the user's ``forward`` runs on a tensor that already has "
"element and quadrature dimensions broadcast-ready; the global assemble is a "
"sparse scatter. The result: assembly is a single GPU kernel."
msgstr ""
"**张量化装配。** 不存在 Python 层面对单元的循环。在 ``__call__`` 内部，基函数和求积点针对整个网格只求值一次；用户的 "
"``forward`` 在一个已经具备单元与求积维度、可直接广播的张量上运行；全局装配则是一次稀疏散射。其结果是：装配就是单个 GPU 内核。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:141 b8b7710035ec43b7a64dbf250f61b10b
msgid ""
"**Differentiable by construction.** ``SparseMatrix.solve`` is a "
":class:`torch.autograd.Function` with a custom backward (an adjoint sparse "
"solve). Gradients therefore flow end-to-end from a loss back through the "
"linear solve, the assembly, and any parameter that touched either — be it a "
"material coefficient, a Dirichlet value, or a neural network's prediction. "
"See :doc:`differentiability`."
msgstr ""
"**生而可微。** ``SparseMatrix.solve`` 是一个带有自定义反向传播（伴随稀疏求解）的 "
":class:`torch.autograd.Function`\\ "
"。因此梯度可以端到端地从损失出发，反向穿过线性求解、装配，以及任何参与其中的参数——无论是材料系数、狄利克雷取值，还是神经网络的预测。参见 "
":doc:`differentiability`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/concepts.rst:148 f1fda19affec4cceb0bf837e0b0d7a11
msgid ""
"**Modular linear algebra.** The solver layer is a separate package, ``torch-"
"sla``. The same FEM code retargets between SciPy (CPU), Eigen (CPU), native "
"PyTorch (CPU/GPU), cuDSS (GPU), and CuPy (GPU) by changing one keyword "
"argument. PETSc and Hypre are on the ``torch-sla`` roadmap; until they ship,"
" fallback paths in :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` provide best-effort support if "
"those libraries are already installed locally."
msgstr ""
"**模块化线性代数。** 求解器层是一个独立的包 ``torch-sla``\\ 。同一份有限元代码只需改动一个关键字参数，即可在 "
"SciPy（CPU）、Eigen（CPU）、原生 PyTorch（CPU/GPU）、cuDSS（GPU）和 CuPy（GPU）之间切换。PETSc 与 "
"Hypre 已列入 ``torch-sla`` 的路线图；在它们正式发布之前，若本地已安装这些库，\\ :mod:`tensormesh.sparse`"
" 中的回退路径会尽力提供支持。"

